name: Blue Ribbon Income Fund
longDescription: The Funds investment objectives are to provide unitholders with high monthly distributions, together with the opportunity for capital appreciation The fund seeks to invests in a high income equity portfolio, consisting primarily of dividend paying Canadian equities.
